{"tid":466763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我終於知道點解龜頭小嘴要追擊肥婆","createTime":"2017-11-13T01:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T10:49:41.000Z","uid":2915,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf40a51df9a0483d10e313d3f177b919dbd0bf1","tid":466763,"uid":2915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:10:47.000Z","msg":"是咁的，係人都知要先落後上架啦<br />\n正當我準備落車嘅時候，個肥婆一野撞入黎<br />\n身為瘦撚嘅我比佢撞左去度門果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家個手臂仲係痺痺地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔知d肥婆到底係咩構造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩唔係夏天，如果唔係真係成手都會被肥婆嘅臭汗同老泥所污染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個肥婆仲要露出一臉不以為意嘅模樣<br />\n經過今次我發現原來肥婆真係一種冇廉恥嘅生物<br />\n<br />\n Btw 又係時候重溫一下肥婆潮文<br />\n<br />\n樣衰唔係罪，係不幸。生得醜唔係你既責任，要怪既，只好怪上帝 <br />\n但係，肥，就係你既錯！ 一個人好地地係唔會肥既，你變得做肥人，梗係食左多過你需要既野啦 係呢個仲有咁多人捱餓既時代，你竟然食咁多野？ 肥係貪心既表現，係唔公平既象徵 肥人臃腫畸形既身體，已經充分顯示出佢地既唔道德 <br />\n<br />\n肥人係罪犯，佢地甚至俾小偷、殺人犯更無恥 一般犯人都會掩飾自己犯左既罪 但係肥人，佢地竟然將自己既罪證放哂響個身上，就好似一個殺人犯拖住條屍周街走咁 你話，見到肥人有乜辦法唔憤怒？ <br />\n<br />\n所以，見到肥人應該即刻鬧佢，就算唔鬧佢都要鄙視佢，我地要透過侮辱黎喚醒佢既良知 係街見到肥人唔鬧佢，就好似搭地鐵見到痴漢非禮學生妹唔出聲一樣 作為一個有良知既人，我地應該出聲，應該股起勇氣挺身而出鬧到佢地狗血淋頭！"},{"pid":"53e595a5a754fd156c786450f79e755b5c2775f2","tid":466763,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:15:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20c253374c4b6663aafca8a9523d3bc68cd37594","tid":466763,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:17:48.000Z","msg":"屌 次次想睇個post都見到條撚樣阻住哂"},{"pid":"9ba06ac49e946c70a5528138030cc53c49402e10","tid":466763,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801450fcd7ab7b13335e412a1987d4bef03a9bc8","tid":466763,"uid":2915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 次次想睇個post都見到條撚樣阻住哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌咪撚就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2663cbedd6c57bcce3fe848f7623d1e20a1caac","tid":466763,"uid":2915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"肥絲大隻呢隻死肥婆真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD肥婆真係通常都冇廉恥 自我中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肥絲就係最好嘅證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4922edae7913846ee0e927f4c9fc890996b764","tid":466763,"uid":2915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:40:43.000Z","msg":"有冇其他人分享下比肥婆迫害嘅經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95233264afed3f07904372d3bf537ecabf37b4f","tid":466763,"uid":128884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:47:44.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"ad6dfaa28575acc46a1152d0395ffccff997a533","tid":466763,"uid":2915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:14:24.000Z","msg":"D肥婆最鐘意做仆街野黎draw attention <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為平時唔會有人想留意佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97bbd640de0b6db717ad818840d8a0446d34ed9","tid":466763,"uid":58002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搭地鐵見到d肥婆真係屌三聲<br />\n強烈建議地鐵收肥婆兩個人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}